userProperties.description: The sub domain of the Dataset
Specify id the dataset is opendata or not
The type of the dataset ordinary/standard
The owner of the dataset. Must be a single user, not an organization.
The format of the Dataset, current supported values are json or csv. If specified there will be a validation of the input file, otherwise the file will be ingested as it is.
Specifies the standard dataset this ordinary dataset is mapped to
